<p>He added: 'The love I feel for this tiny human is beyond my understanding. Grateful to know her, proud to call her mine, and thankful for the life we will have together x.' </p>

<p>Family sources leaked word of the pregnancy in April and at the end of the month Gigi confirmed the news herself on The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon.</p>

<p>But it hasn't been all family time for Bella, as she is gearing up for a new work project.</p>

